  "text": "As we mentioned in [CITATION_1] , efficiency gains in MC estimation of the hypervolume over time may be obtained by retaining a memory of those samples non-dominated at the previous time step (though we did not provide a formal description of such a process in [CITATION_2] ). We detail a number of improvements and extensions to this idea in the following sections.",
